                    <span>I found the writer, Crane, dying to interpose his bad poetry, bad jokes and whining, obnoxious self into what could have been a thoughtful story about a monk and his religious beliefs. Too bad!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Read it!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
